{"word":"μολυβδίς","slug":"μολυβδίς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μολυβδίς</b></el> <el>(μολυβδίς, ίδος, ἡ,) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a leaden weight</i> on a net, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>like <a href='S:μολύβδαινα'><el>μολύβδαινα</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>a leaden ball</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:μόλυβδος'><el>μόλυβδος</el></a>\n"}]}